'''DNALinux''' is a [[Linux distribution]] with [[bioinformatics]] software included. It is a [[Live CD]]. It is based on [[Slax]] but includes programs like [[BLAST]] and [http://www.emboss.org/ EMBOSS]. DNALinux is made by [http://www.genesdigitales.com/ Genes Digitales] and [http://www.unq.edu.ar/ Quilmes National University], Argentina.
